# Retail Store SQL Analysis

## Overview

Analyzed a retail store database using SQL to understand customer behavior, product performance, order trends, payment patterns, and business performance metrics.

## Database Tables

- Customers
- Orders
- Order Items
- Products
- Product Reviews
- Payments

## SQL Skills Demonstrated

- SELECT Statements
- WHERE Clauses
- GROUP BY
- ORDER BY
- Aggregate Functions
- Joins
- Subqueries
- Business Analysis

## Key Analysis

- Customer purchasing behavior
- Product performance analysis
- Revenue insights
- Payment trends
- Product review analysis

## Tools Used

- SQL
- MySQL
- Database Management
- Data Analysis

## Files

- retail_store_customers.sql
- retail_store_orders.sql
- retail_store_order_items.sql
- retail_store_products.sql
- retail_store_product_reviews.sql
- retail_store_payments.sql
